ile the <a href=\"https://www.fizik.com/us_en/gravita-versor-flat.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Versor</a> (right, $139.99) is a lightweight trail shoe designed for DH park laps. Both shoes come in three colorways and would be great candidates for all-mountain activities. See more at <a href=\"https://www.fizik.com/us_en/shop/shoes/off-road/downhill.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fizik</a>.</p>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"d9a05331adc31032d64411798a68e8dca33acbc60181972c6320503c25896ef4","category":"Cycling"}